---
// CompoundingSection.astro - Before / Mechanism / After comparison
---

<section class="compounding-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="compounding-header">
      <h2>Your Revenue Stack, Compounding</h2>
      <p>A revenue engine that gets smarter every time it runs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="compounding-grid">
      <!-- Column 1: Before -->
      <div class="compounding-card">
        <span class="card-label">Without Inform Growth</span>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Every question starts from zero</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> CRM data means different things to different teams</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> New hires take months to get context</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Manual cleanup never catches up</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2: The System (accented) -->
      <div class="compounding-card accent">
        <span class="card-label">What we build</span>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> One governed AI layer across your stack</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Field definitions written once, used everywhere</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Workflows codify into tools - costs fall over time</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Every new tool makes the next one faster</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3: After -->
      <div class="compounding-card">
        <span class="card-label">With Inform Growth</span>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Revenue questions answered in minutes</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> One source of truth every team trusts</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> New tools and hires inherit full context</li>
          <li><span class="list-marker">■</span> Value accumulates - the system learns</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="compounding-tagline">Faster decisions · Cleaner data · Shared infrastructure</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .compounding-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .compounding-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
  }

  .compounding-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .compounding-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .compounding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .compounding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .compounding-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
  }

  .compounding-card.accent {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .compounding-card.accent .card-label {
    color: #FFFFFF;
    border-bottom-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }

  .compounding-card.accent .card-list li {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .compounding-card.accent .list-marker {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .card-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .card-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .card-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .list-marker {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 5px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .compounding-tagline {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
